Paul H [10:26 PM]
Copy this:
```RWHZSIKINCSNHVALEATUVFHYOMAMUXZ9IFNPCYNP9ESWPSGTHOBRIIOMKENTQLTNFFCISPMGTDRHKMPRA```
into this```
999999999999999999999999999999999999999999999999999999999999999999999999999999999HLEZIZZLYVFGTDDEPM9O9UYKVKACBLZZWTXTRKUDVZ9CRCGVDVJDOGCIGSLXCZKNRXGXG9AQNPSERNZUHXMVTPTZGDKZBVLIRREMFUCIIJBZX9TTXEOPIGCEZBCPWCXBJRDDKVLTDMRPBZIYTLBQGTUEULIFOVWXLZ```
to give you this```RWHZSIKINCSNHVALEATUVFHYOMAMUXZ9IFNPCYNP9ESWPSGTHOBRIIOMKENTQLTNFFCISPMGTDRHKMPRAHLEZIZZLYVFGTDDEPM9O9UYKVKACBLZZWTXTRKUDVZ9CRCGVDVJDOGCIGSLXCZKNRXGXG9AQNPSERNZUHXMVTPTZGDKZBVLIRREMFUCIIJBZX9TTXEOPIGCEZBCPWCXBJRDDKVLTDMRPBZIYTLBQGTUEULIFOVWXLZ
```You transform, which may give you this: ```GXAZLARHLFKRTMGHN9OAZZDRRHIJN9JTL9SLPYIPDSGWTMTVAGVZUZP9VMZHAHQLWHMAUUPXAVII99999YWEL9EGBCCBZSCKZOKIXOEMJBUVRXRBKBWVB9ACRTTPKVOZYNGUB9VKBPUHLKJKMEFCTVEJNXNYHRWEDROEQIDGXXOYHMXIFBKYXOWJ9YWGOGLHXOLCWPIIALVHXRPBIOOERZNRMZXPEXWB9HDLLAILMCIIIM9QACU
```
You grab the first 243 trits/81trytes to get this:
```GXAZLARHLFKRTMGHN9OAZZDRRHIJN9JTL9SLPYIPDSGWTMTVAGVZUZP9VMZHAHQLWHMAUUPXAVII99999```
see all those 9's? those are trits with value 0

